race.comment: SETTLE FOR LESS (2) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (25.70) last time out at this track. Form at the trip sound including two wins. Can find winning form. DAPPER CHAP (1) was quickly into stride and burnt early from the middle draw where he gave a sight, finishing third (29.58) and beaten 3.5 lengths over 515m at Sandown. Can feature again. HERE COMES JOJO (6) has a strong record here with three wins and a minor from six starts. Was out of placings last time (26.29) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing fifth and beaten 3.5 lengths. Looks suited here and can measure up. HEY PRESTO (4) racing over this course and distance brings the best out in her.
